sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant HTTP as vLLM HTTP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA
    participant S3 as S3 / Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Engine,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    Engine->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / access key
    S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>GPU: Load model into GPU memory<br/>CUDA

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    RBAC->>HTTP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 (localhost)<br/>Auth: None
    HTTP->>Engine: Process inference
    Engine->>GPU: GPU compute (CUDA)
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>HTTP: Completion response
    HTTP-->>RBAC: JSON response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: JSON response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS-compatible)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC GenerationService<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    RBAC->>TGIS: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>Auth: None
    TGIS->>Engine: In-process call (Python)
    Engine->>GPU: GPU compute (CUDA)
    GPU-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>TGIS: Generation result
    TGIS-->>RBAC: gRPC response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: gRPC response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response
